headline: Agilent Ranks No. 11 on Fortune’s List of Best Workplaces in the World
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., November 19, 2024--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced the company has been named to Fortune’s list of Best Workplaces in the World, ranking no. 11 among 25 companies.
